  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The objective of the RM-TF is dual:
-	Improve domestic tax revenue performance in RM-TF beneficiary countries
-	 Improve taxpayer compliance in RM-TF beneficiary countries.

The MFA will base future support on progress attained in the implementation of the engagement as described in the IMF program document. Progress will be measured through the IMF&#xB4;s monitoring framework.
For Danida&#x2019;s reporting purposes the following key outcome and output indicators have been selected to document progress: 
-	Average tax to GDP ratio trends in RM-TF beneficiary countries.
-	Average tax gaps reduced over time in RM-TF beneficiary countries (for countries where this indicator is measured).</narrative>
  </description>
